<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Sajha Pasal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mailTemplate.css">  <!-- External CSS -->
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome <strong>{{userName}}</strong> to Sajha Pasal!</h1>
        <p>We're excited to have you as part of our growing community.</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <p>Congratulations on your successful registration! We are thrilled to have you with us.</p>
